{
  "stem": "7598.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And fortunately, all went off well and we weren't bothered or blackmailed later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we finally received this transit visa, which was in April 1942, my brother and I left Nice on our own, with my uncle and aunt, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the hope of getting to Portugal within two days and getting our visa at the Belgian consulate and then getting to England.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went to Perpignan and from Perpignan we took the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we got to the Spanish frontier-- I mustn't forget the Spanish were great fascists.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Franco really was not a very nice human being.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were stopped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our visa wasn't valid, they said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the stamp didn't say that the transit for 48 hours-- was for 48 hours only.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We then tracked back by thumbing a lift back to Perpignan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we got to the-- How did you travel?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went by train to Nice, to the frontier, but then the authorities wouldn't let us through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went back to Perpignan, where there was a consul.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was late in the evening and the consulate was just about to close.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I must have been fairly controlled up to now, but I burst into tears.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother, in a very controlled fashion, sort of told me to pull myself together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then for some mysterious reason, they opened the door and let us go upstairs to the consulate, at which point my brother nudged me and said, this is the time to cry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, we got the extra 48 hours only.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I suspect that even Fascists and Nazis, some of them were sorry for children.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
